      • getCodonsStartingFrom

        public String getCodonsStartingFrom(TranscriptPosition txPos,
                                    CDSPosition cdsPos,
                                    int count)
        Returns a number of codons (String of length 3 * len) starting from the affected one by the change at txPos/cdsPos. If there is not a sufficient number of nucleotides in the transcript string then return fewer, only up to the end.
        Parameters:
        txPos - transcript position of the change
        cdsPos - CDS position of the change
        count - number of codons to return
        Returns:
        the codon affected by a change at the given position
